  "texts": [
    "He is the co-founder of iRobot Corp., which is the maker of the Roomba vacuum cleaning robot.",
    "Brooks also served as the director of the MIT Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence Laboratory, and is known for his influential work in behavior-based robotics. 3.",
    "Cynthia Breazeal: Cynthia Breazeal is an American roboticist and professor, widely known for her work in social robotics and human-robot interaction.",
    "She is the director of the Personal Robots Group at the MIT Media Lab, where she created the world's first social robot, Kismet, in 1997.",
    "Breazeal's work focuses on developing robots that can communicate and interact with people in a more human-like way, and she has received numerous awards for her research in this field."
